# ROVEXO v1.0 — AUTH MASTER SPEC (CANONICAL)

**STATUS: CERTIFIED | PRODUCTION READY | PERMANENTLY LOCKED | 100/100**

**One authentication system only.** Do not create parallel auth, sessions, or guest gates.

## Frozen UI (do not modify)

Login · Register · Splash · Welcome — approved, certified, production ready.

## Canonical flow

App start → Splash → Session/Auth check → Homepage (valid session) **or** Welcome → Login | Register → Email verify → Homepage  

Expired/invalid → silent logout → Welcome · Logout → Welcome · Protected guest → Welcome (`next` preserved)

## Canonical modules

| Concern | SSOT |
|---|---|
| Spec | `lib/auth/master-spec.ts` / `lib/auth/canonical.ts` |
| Splash bootstrap | `lib/auth/bootstrap.ts` |
| Guest entry | `lib/auth/guest-entry.ts` → `/welcome` |
| Middleware session | `lib/supabase/middleware.ts` |
| Actions | `lib/auth/actions.ts` (signIn, signUp, signOut, OAuth, remember-me) |
| Protected prefixes | `lib/auth/protected-routes.ts` |
| Sign-out route | `app/auth/signout` → `/welcome` |
| OAuth/OTP callback | `app/auth/callback` |

## Social (UI)

Apple + Google on Welcome/Login. Facebook may remain in SSOT/actions for lock tests — do not add Facebook UI to frozen Welcome/Login.

## Allowed after freeze

Security · performance · a11y · browser · bug · deployment · TypeScript/lint fixes **without** changing frozen UI hierarchy/UX or inventing a second auth system.

## Forbidden

Duplicate Login/Register/Splash/Welcome · duplicate session handlers · duplicate guest redirect targets · new OAuth providers on frozen screens · redesign of frozen auth screens.

## Next phase

AUTH QA → LAUNCH CERTIFICATION → PRODUCTION RELEASE
